description: Global Hemp Group Inc. engages in the production and processing of industrial hemp in the United States. It focuses on the development of sustainable and green value-added industrial hemp products utilizing the processing of the hemp plant for multi-merchantable applications. The company was formerly known as Arris Holdings Inc. and changed its name to Global Hemp Group Inc. in March 2014. Global Hemp Group Inc. was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in North Vancouver, Canada.
